==Latin==
===Suffix===
'''-ivus''', '''[[-iva]]''', '''[[-ivum]]'''

# adjective suffix, often added to the perfect passive participle of verbs

Example:

{| border="1" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0"
|-----
! Verb
! Perfect Passive Participle
! Adjective
|-----
| agere || actus || activus
|-----
| stare || status || stativus
|}
